Title: Weekly: Heading Out
Descriptions: This is Rico, the relentless force that don't back down. You think you got what it takes to earn your keep? Well, here's your chance to prove it. I'm laying down the law, and it's a tough one: 100 headshots. Yeah, you heard me right. 100 bandit skulls to bring me. I ain't sugar-coating it. I'm giving it to you straight. You want the rewards? You want the respect? Then you gotta earn it. And there's no easy way out. Survivors, you wanna survive in this unforgiving world? You gotta show me you got the grit, the skill, and the sheer determination to make it happen. No excuses. So get out there, track 'em down, and make every shot count. Bring me those bandit heads, and maybe, just maybe, you'll earn yourself a spot in this brutal landscape. Rico, out.
